arStrings.szText: This confirms my suspicions! The Ennead clan magically shackled these creatures with ensorcelled armor to bolster their own armies during the mage clan wars!
It seems that the creatures outlived their masters in the end. Is this the reason they can conjure this dark magic? Hmm. I'd like to investigate further.
If the magic runs as deep as I suspect, I'll need to examine not only their armor but their remains as well. Some of their eyes and hearts will do.
I have some preparations to make. There is a clearing nearby. Meet me there once you've gathered the items.
